@Logistics.Services.Inventory.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:51005
@SkuId = SKU-HTTP-001
@ExternalOrderNo = ERP-HTTP-001
@ReleaseReservationId = replace-with-release-reservation-id
@DeductReservationId = replace-with-deduct-reservation-id
@MissingReservationId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

### 查询 SKU 库存总账
GET {{Logistics.Services.Inventory.Api_HostAddress}}/api/inventory/skus/{{SkuId}}

### 调整库存
POST {{Logistics.Services.Inventory.Api_HostAddress}}/api/inventory/adjustments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "skuId": "{{SkuId}}",
  "quantityDelta": 100,
  "referenceNo": "INITIAL-STOCK"
}

### 锁定库存
POST {{Logistics.Services.Inventory.Api_HostAddress}}/api/inventory/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "skuId": "{{SkuId}}",
  "externalOrderNo": "{{ExternalOrderNo}}",
  "quantity": 30
}

### 释放库存预留
POST {{Logistics.Services.Inventory.Api_HostAddress}}/api/inventory/reservations/{{ReleaseReservationId}}/release

### 扣减库存预留
POST {{Logistics.Services.Inventory.Api_HostAddress}}/api/inventory/reservations/{{DeductReservationId}}/deduct

### 失败场景：SKU 为空，应该返回 400
POST {{Logistics.Services.Inventory.Api_HostAddress}}/api/inventory/adjustments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "skuId": " ",
  "quantityDelta": 10,
  "referenceNo": "BAD-SKU"
}

### 失败场景：调整数量为 0，应该返回 400
POST {{Logistics.Services.Inventory.Api_HostAddress}}/api/inventory/adjustments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "skuId": "{{SkuId}}",
  "quantityDelta": 0,
  "referenceNo": "ZERO-DELTA"
}

### 失败场景：锁定数量超过可用库存，应该返回 400
POST {{Logistics.Services.Inventory.Api_HostAddress}}/api/inventory/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "skuId": "{{SkuId}}",
  "externalOrderNo": "ERP-HTTP-NOT-ENOUGH",
  "quantity": 999999
}

### 失败场景：库存预留不存在，释放应该返回 404
POST {{Logistics.Services.Inventory.Api_HostAddress}}/api/inventory/reservations/{{MissingReservationId}}/release

### 失败场景：库存预留 ID 为空，扣减应该返回 400
POST {{Logistics.Services.Inventory.Api_HostAddress}}/api/inventory/reservations/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/deduct
